<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 8px; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .header { background-color: #059669; color: white; padding: 15px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Welcome to CoffeeShop!</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p>Welcome to our Coffee Shop! We are thrilled to have you here.</p>
        <p>Feel free to browse our menu and place your first order today.</p>
        <br/>
        <p>Best regards,<br/>The Coffee Shop Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>